Package repast.simphony.ws.gis

Class StyledLayerGIS

java.lang.Object
repast.simphony.ws.gis.StyledLayerGIS
public class StyledLayerGIS extends Object
Layer for GIS Display Server. Note that GIS displays use a NullLayout since the geography context is directly queried for the agent positions.
Author:
Eric Tatara
